rows.label: qst702406_msg0001
rows.name: What do you want with me...?

rows.label: qst702406_msg0002
rows.name:
You want to know if I'm interested
in joining the resistance...?

rows.label: qst702406_msg0004
rows.name:
Besides, I have things to
do in this city... Sorry,
but please look elsewhere.

rows.label: qst702406_msg0005
rows.name: Hmm? You still want my skills...?

rows.label: qst702406_msg0006
rows.name:
If you put it that way, I
can't just turn you down.

rows.label: qst702406_msg0007
rows.name:
Alright... I'll think about it.
But don't get your hopes up.

rows.label: qst702406_msg0101
rows.name:
For the sake of your passion,
I'll think about it.

rows.label: qst702406_msg0102
rows.name:
If, by some chance, I feel like it,
I'll go to the resistance camp.

rows.label: qst702406_msg0103
rows.name: But don't get your hopes up.
